Package: uniform
Type: Package
Title: Unification of a Differently or Incompletely Reported Continuous Outcome across Studies Included in a Meta-Analysis
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Benjamin", "Kendziora", email = benjamin.kendziora@med.uni-muenchen.de",role=c("cre","aut")),
    person("Lorenz", "Uhlmann", role=c("ctb"))
Maintainer: Benjamin Kendziora, M.D., Ph.D. <benjamin.kendziora@med.uni-muenchen.de>
Description: Allows to uniform a differently or incompletely reported continuous outcome across studies included in a meta-analysis. Unification includes conversion and imputation methods. The main function co.co returns mean and standard deviation for all groups of observation units. Other functions allow to calculate effect measures for each study.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/bkendzio/uniform
BugReports: https://github.com/bkendzio/uniform/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 4.2.2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
